review_title: Really fun game but game breaking issue
one_reviews_text: I really love this game and I really want to keep playing but this glitch keeps happening where after a certain point in the level my guy doesn't want to jump over objects anymore and I'm just stuck there trying my hardest to jump over but can't. The game is fun but I really would love for this bug to be fixed so I can play more.
Outstanding game with crazy puzzle levels!
